Package: zzedc.validation
Type: Package
Title: Validation DSL for Clinical Trial Data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ronald G. Thomas", email = "rgthomas@ucsd.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Ronald G. Thomas [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Ronald G. Thomas <rgthomas@ucsd.edu>
Description: A domain-specific language (DSL) for writing clinical trial data validation rules.
    Supports real-time field-level validation and batch quality control checks.
    Features include cross-field validation, conditional logic, date arithmetic, and
    clinical trial-specific patterns. Can compile to both R (for real-time Shiny apps)
    and SQL (for nightly batch QC).
